summary: Comprehensive detailed exports and structural comparison of all 8 Relume projects. Includes full text exports for MezTa 8 (30+ pages, 12 Solutions) and MezTal 5 (25-30 pages, 9 Solutions + EOR) showing wireframe component breakdowns, page hierarchies, and content guidance. Compares all projects across Solutions count, Industries count, total pages, structure type, and key features. Highlights MezTa 8's advantages: most comprehensive Solutions coverage including Sales and Design, most detailed wireframe specifications, highest total page count, and best content integration with testimonials. Provides recommendation matrix for MezTa 8 vs MezTal 5 selection with trade-offs, verification needs, and action items for each option.
